<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

body {
    font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #e2e8f0;
    background-color: #1a202c;
    overflow-x: hidden;
}

nav {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2b6cb0, #ed8936);
    padding: 1.3rem 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 1000;
}

.nav-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
}

.logo {
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 1.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: 0.8px;
}

.nav-links {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
}

.nav-links li a {
    color: #fff;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    position: relative;
}

.nav-links li a:hover {
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
}

.nav-links li a::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    width: 0;
    height: 2px;
    background: #ed8936;
    bottom: -3px;
    left: 50%;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
}

.nav-links li a:hover::after {
    width: 60%;
}

.hero-section {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(43, 108, 176, 0.1), rgba(237, 137, 54, 0.1));
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
}

.hero-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -40%;
    left: -40%;
    width: 180%;
    height: 180%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1), transparent);
    animation: rotate 30s linear infinite;
}

.hero-section h1 {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 1.3rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    animation: slideIn 0.9s ease-out;
}

.hero-section h1 span {
    color: #ed8936;
}

.hero-section p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #cbd5e0;
    max-width: 750px;
    margin: 0 auto 1.8rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    animation: fadeIn 1.1s ease-out;
}

.hero-section a {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #ed8936;
    color: #fff;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 0.9rem 2.2rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
}

.hero-section a:hover {
    background: #2b6cb0;
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
}

.features-section {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 3.5rem auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
}

.features-section h2 {
    font-size: 2.3rem;
    color: #fff;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    animation: slideIn 0.9s ease-out;
}

.features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(270px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.8rem;
}

.feature-card {
    background: #2d3748;
    padding: 1.8rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    text-align: center;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    animation: fadeInUp 1.2s ease-out;
}

.feature-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
}

.feature-card img {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 130px;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 1.3rem;
}

.feature-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: #ed8936;
    margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
}

.feature-card p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #cbd5e0;
}

.testimonial-section {
    margin: 4.5rem 0;
    padding: 2.8rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2b6cb0, #ed8936);
    color: #fff;
    border-radius: 12px;
    text-align: center;
    animation: fadeIn 1.6s ease-out;
}

.testimonial-section h2 {
    font-size: 2.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
}

.testimonial-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(290px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.8rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
}

.testimonial-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    padding: 1.8rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    animation: fadeInUp 1.4s ease-out;
}

.testimonial-card p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
}

.testimonial-card h4 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 500;
}

@keyframes slideIn {
    from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(-25px);
    }
    to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
    }
}

@keyframes fadeInUp {
    from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(35px);
    }
    to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
    }
}

@keyframes fadeIn {
    from {
        opacity: 0;
    }
    to {
        opacity: 1;
    }
}

@keyframes rotate {
    from {
        transform: rotate(0deg);
    }
    to {
        transform: rotate(360deg);
    }
}

@media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .features-grid,
    .testimonial-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-section h1 {
        font-size: 2.6rem;
    }

    .hero-section p {
        font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .nav-links {
        gap: 0.9rem;
    }

    .nav-links li a {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        padding: 0.4rem 0.7rem;
    }

    .features-section h2,
    .testimonial-section h2 {
        font-size: 1.9rem;
    }
}
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <div class="nav-container">
            <a href="/" class="logo">MySite</a>
            <ul class="nav-links">
                <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
                <li><a href="/services">Services</a></li>
                <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <section class="hero-section">
        <h1>Welcome to <span>MySite</span></h1>
        <p>Unlock your business potential with our innovative solutions, designed to inspire growth and deliver exceptional results.</p>
        <a href="/services">Explore Our Services</a>
    </section>

    <section class="features-section">
        <h2>Why Choose Us</h2>
        <div class="features-grid">
            <div class="feature-card">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" alt="Innovation">
                <h3>Innovation</h3>
                <p>We leverage cutting-edge technology to create solutions that keep you ahead of the curve.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" alt="Expertise">
                <h3>Expertise</h3>
                <p>Our team of professionals brings years of experience to deliver top-notch results.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" alt="Support">
                <h3>Support</h3>
                <p>We provide dedicated support to ensure your success every step of the way.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="testimonial-section">
        <h2>What Our Clients Say</h2>
        <div class="testimonial-grid">
            <div class="testimonial-card">
                <p>"MySite transformed our online presence with a stunning website and effective marketing strategies."</p>
                <h4>Alice Johnson, CEO</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-card">
                <p>"Their cloud solutions streamlined our operations, saving us time and resources."</p>
                <h4>Michael Lee, CTO</h4>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</body>
</html>